In this paper, requirements for designing such an architecture were derived from Industrie 4.0 standards and literature. As a main contribution of this paper, a reference architecture for big data and machine learning in industrial automation has been proposed, which complies with the Reference Architecture Model for Industrie 4.0. In order to evaluate the conceptual architecture, it has been implemented in the SmartFactoryOWL where the performance and scalabil- ity have been examined on industrial data.
